gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 133, Spurs 123
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeated the Spurs, 133-123. Joel Embiid recorded a career-high 70 points, along with 18 rebounds and five assists for the 76ers, with Tyrese Maxey adding 18 points and eight assists in the victory. Victor Wembanyama tallied 33 points and seven rebounds for the Spurs in the losing effort. The 76ers improve to 29-13, while the Spurs fall to 8-35.
